entry.title: 瞎写CNN中遇到的问题
entry.content:
问题：Expected 2D (unbatched) or 3D (batched) input to conv1d, but got input of size: [12]
原因：输入转换成3维向量reshape(1,1,-1)

问题：’MSELoss’ object has no attribute ‘backward’
原因：criterion = nn.MSELoss() 忘了写()

问题：y_pred在CNN里跑了一遍没有值是none
原因：网络forward忘了写return 玛德

问题：loss = criterion(y_pred,y_train) Found dtype Double but expected Float
原因：loss = criterion(a,b) a b 两个一个是float32一个是float64不统一
